'''Khadiijo''' ([[ingiriis]]: Khadija; [[carabi]]: ﺧﺪﻳﺠﺔ ﺑﻨﺖ ﺧﻮﻳﻠﺪ, "Khadiija bintu Khuwaylid"; lagu naaneysi jirey: Khadīja al-Kubra "Khadija weynayd") ku dhalatey magaalada [[Makka]], [[Xijaas]]<ref>"[[ingiriis]]: Khadija; [[carabi]]: ﺧﺪﻳﺠﺔ ﺑﻨﺖ ﺧﻮﻳﻠﺪ, "Khadiija bintu Khuwaylid"; lagu naaneysi jirey: Khadīja al-Kubra "Khadija weynayd""</ref><ref>"[[Makka]], [[Xijaas]], dhulka [[Carabi]]ya"</ref> ee dhulka [[Carabi]]ya markey taariikhdu ahayd [[sanad|sanadkii 555]] [[C.D]], kuna dhimatay magaalada Makka [[wakhti|sanadkii 620]] [[C.D]] waa [[oori]]dii kowaad ee [[Nebi Muxamed]] [[File:Mohamed peace be upon him.svg|18px]] (n.n.k.h) qoftaasi oo ahayd [[ganacsi|ganacsato]]<ref>"[[sanad|sanadkii 555]] [[C.D]], [[wakhti|sanadkii 620]] [[C.D]] waa [[oori]]dii kowaad ee [[Nebi Muxamed]]"</ref> si fiican looga yaqaano magaalada [[Makka]] ee deegaanka [[Xijaas]].<ref>"magaalada [[Makka]] ee deegaanka [[Xijaas]]"</ref> 

Khadiijo waxay ahayd qofkii ugu horeeyay ee rumeeysa [[Nebi]]ga[[File:Mohamed peace be upon him.svg|18px]] markii uu waxyiga [[diin]]ta [[Islaam]]ku ku soo degay. 
[[Dad]]ka [[muslim]]iinta ahi waxay u yaqaanaan Khadiija ineey tahay “'''Hooyada Islaamka'''”.<ref>"qofkii ugu horeeyay ee rumeeysa [[Nebi]]ga markii uu waxyiga [[diin]]ta [[Islaam]]"</ref><ref>"[[Dad]]ka [[muslim]]iinta ahi waxay u yaqaanaan Khadiija ineey tahay “'''Hooyada Islaamka'''”"</ref>

